                  <br></br>
                  <p>This is going to be your first code review. A code review a simply a review of a program or piece of code you will be writing. During bootcamp these occur at least once a week. They aren't meant to "mark" your work but rather give you an opportunity to get feedback on your code.</p>
                  <br></br>
                  <p>For you first assignment you will be building a recipe page.</p>
                  <p>You have full creative control to build anything you would like, using any tools you would like. Feel free to go through some of the stretch goals at the end of this section of the course. There will be many useful tools and videos you can watch that will help you build this project.</p>
                  <br></br>
                  <h3>Requirements</h3>
                  <br></br>
              </div>
              <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2">

                  <p>Your code must contain all of the following tags:</p>
                  <ul class="ul_intro">
